How to Install:

Download the latest version of the preset.

Then move the preset into C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
if your plugins folder does not have a CharGen or Preset Folder just Make one.

Launch the game load in the preset and have fun!!!!
